      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783529497568,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Do your own work within iterations iteratively.\n    - Before you write a line of code, decide how you'll know that part is \"done\".\n    - Break your work into chunks of things you need to \"figure out\".\n    - If it takes you more than X amount of time to figure it out, break it down further.\n    - When you have it figured out, start looking for failure modes. How could this break?\n    - How could I make it simpler?\n    - Repeat as necessary for the rest of your life.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Do your own work within iterations iteratively.\n    - Before you write a line of code, decide how you'll know that part is \"done\".\n    - Break your work into chunks of things you need to \"figure out\".\n    - If it takes you more than X amount of time to figure it out, break it down further.\n    - When you have it figured out, start looking for failure modes. How could this break?\n    - How could I make it simpler?\n    - Repeat as necessary for the rest of your life.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
